Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.47,0:07:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身…身體動不了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.18,0:07:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，不能過去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.35,0:08:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快動，快動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.66,0:08:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ…ちぃ她…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.10,0:08:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.27,0:08:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倉庫？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.74,0:08:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為最近東西容易發霉潮濕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.14,0:08:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原本想來個大掃除
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是電燈泡快要壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直沒辦法打掃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了換燈泡\N我找來了各種東西墊腳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.75,0:08:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我還是碰不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會叫我來幫忙換
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.43,0:08:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.73,0:08:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是從門下面\N流出的黑色液體…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.03,0:08:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，我搬桌子的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.47,0:08:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不小心打翻了水桶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.54,0:08:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時候我有上去找本須和幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.34,0:08:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過你看起來好像很忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.04,0:09:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電燈泡、桌子、水桶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過為什麼會有104號房？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.72,0:09:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來一樓本來有四間房間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.72,0:09:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隔壁是103號房
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.06,0:09:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我搬來時做了一點改裝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.43,0:09:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,缺的是102號房
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.47,0:09:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然被搞得團團轉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是丟臉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.94,0:09:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經不害怕了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全不怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.91,0:09:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.20,0:09:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.27,0:09:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大魔王終於登場了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.17,0:10:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是打不倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他那麼強嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.44,0:10:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.64,0:10:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看雜誌和網路上的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒看過有人打倒過他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.35,0:10:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警告，警告
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.68,0:10:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通過這裡就可以到下個城鎮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.69,0:10:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，你是認真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.36,0:10:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別想不開了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.49,0:10:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是打不贏那傢伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.96,0:10:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.89,0:10:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ她…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ她也許正在等我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.37,0:10:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.80,0:10:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿他沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.77,0:10:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.51,0:10:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.14,0:10:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,carbonara
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.08,0:10:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,chorizo
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.83,0:11:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.07,0:11:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經不行了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.42,0:11:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ち…ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.75,0:11:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時ちぃ明明沒有經驗值
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.12,0:11:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻打倒了遊戲裡的大魔王吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.29,0:11:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和也不可能會寫這種程式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.83,0:12:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道她真的不是普通的電腦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.81,0:12:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.43,0:12:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.79,0:12:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛那個妳有看到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.50,0:12:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹看到海豚的“嘩啦”\N會很高興嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.10,0:12:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.47,0:12:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，妳看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.07,0:12:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.21,0:12:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.18,0:12:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.51,0:12:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高興
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.75,0:13:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ也要來嘩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.06,0:13:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.87,0:13:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是不會游泳嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ち…ちぃ呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.82,0:14:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.36,0:14:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來妳沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.39,0:14:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.06,0:14:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從表面看來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.40,0:14:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像也沒進水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，你在生氣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.07,0:14:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ做錯事了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會生氣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.91,0:14:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.48,0:14:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.75,0:14:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖說如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.15,0:14:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她真是台不可思議的電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.32,0:14:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般如果掉到海裡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.45,0:14:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會進水，然後會很難修復
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ的相關記憶資料到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:14:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光靠我們果然還是\N有點資料不足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找新保幫忙看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.41,0:15:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.64,0:15:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過新保少爺他…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.62,0:15:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保，新保
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.99,0:15:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今天先出門了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.63,0:15:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.77,0:15:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嚴重的黑眼圈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.80,0:15:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,熬夜了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.01,0:15:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.95,0:15:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好像也很睏的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事實上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.29,0:15:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清…清水老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.85,0:15:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我住一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.96,0:15:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.33,0:15:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然叫那麼大聲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.57,0:16:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家回到座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.84,0:16:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要開始上課了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.51,0:16:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師還沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.61,0:16:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有時會早到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.01,0:16:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是她從來沒遲到過的說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.91,0:16:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.22,0:16:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有電話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.22,0:16:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫我接通
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.52,0:16:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.72,0:16:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.63,0:17:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.70,0:17:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個聲音，你是新保對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.70,0:17:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在在搞什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.87,0:17:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟老師私奔…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.36,0:17:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.62,0:17:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們吵架了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.33,0:17:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.23,0:17:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們很久沒有吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者應該說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.74,0:17:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連話都說不上兩句
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.88,0:17:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上了門鍊就表示
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.91,0:17:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我老公忘了我會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.66,0:18:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.16,0:18:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在不在家都沒影響了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.86,0:18:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一想到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就覺得怎樣都無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.54,0:18:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,覺得怎樣都…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明在說這麼傷心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.82,0:18:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她卻沒有哭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.56,0:18:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.89,0:18:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.33,0:18:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她其實很想哭出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.96,0:18:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是拼命在忍耐罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.67,0:18:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想至少讓她在遇到\N不愉快或傷心的事時
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.87,0:18:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠哭個痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.74,0:18:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我迷上她了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.85,0:19:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此，為什麼要私奔？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.05,0:19:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道只剩這個方法了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.59,0:19:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我們這個年紀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.19,0:19:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是小鬼而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.42,0:19:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以後你打算怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.72,0:19:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.09,0:19:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許就如同你所說的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.79,0:19:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.03,0:19:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這是我的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決定？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.30,0:19:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多香子她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.67,0:19:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變得不相信男人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.27,0:19:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她認為就算一開始說喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.94,0:19:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦出現像電腦那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.54,0:19:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以迎合自己的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.18,0:19:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會完全改變
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.05,0:19:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像從沒喜歡過一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.42,0:19:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.62,0:19:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.92,0:19:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓她跑掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決定私奔到深山的溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.96,0:19:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是個好地方喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.06,0:19:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣濕答答的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.53,0:19:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不過是旅行而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.03,0:19:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩恩愛愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.36,0:19:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說，這算是私奔啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.47,0:19:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.64,0:19:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在多香子點頭之前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.07,0:19:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不打算回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.34,0:19:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,點頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.54,0:20:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.77,0:20:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我再婚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.34,0:20:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再婚？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.11,0:20:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再婚，再婚…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.21,0:20:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再婚是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.18,0:20:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.11,0:20:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉再幫我保管一段時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.72,0:20:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫你保管當然沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.22,0:20:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜囉，本須和
